00:21:46,800 --> 00:21:54,880
♫   Because of you, it&nbsp;has rusted&nbsp;  ♫

228
00:21:54,880 --> 00:22:00,530
♫   What do I do with myself?&nbsp;  ♫

229
00:22:01,560 --> 00:22:08,080
♫  &nbsp;It's because my chest feels tight   ♫

230
00:22:08,080 --> 00:22:15,880
♫   I feel frustrated because my chest feels tight   ♫

231
