♫   No matter how much I hit until I get bruised,&nbsp;  ♫

232
00:22:22,880 --> 00:22:27,840
♫   &nbsp;You spread across my heart   ♫

233
00:22:27,840 --> 00:22:34,450
♫   Love is so mean   ♫

234
