♫   &nbsp;Why do you keep shaking up my heart?&nbsp;  ♫

235
00:22:42,270 --> 00:22:49,550
♫   As much as it is sad, this mean love   ♫

236
00:22:49,550 --> 00:22:55,780
♫   You don't know it yet   ♫

237
00:23:10,550 --> 00:23:12,150
Halt!

238
00:23:14,060 --> 00:23:16,190
Drop your swords!

239
00:23:17,920 --> 00:23:22,170
Your Highness, what brings you here?

240
00:23:28,280 --> 00:23:29,740
Where is my uncle?

241
00:23:29,740 --> 00:23:31,870
Please come this way.

242
00:23:43,870 --> 00:23:47,880
My nephew! What are you doing here?

243
00:23:49,460 --> 00:23:51,350
Did something happen in the capital?

244
00:23:51,350 --> 00:23:53,620
I think Eun Seong brought a woman here in secret.

245
00:23:53,620 --> 00:23:55,240
A woman in our campaign?

246
00:23:55,240 --> 00:23:57,770
In order to take care of it before it became a crisis,

247
00:23:57,770 --> 00:24:00,520
I rode on horseback all night to follow you.

248
00:24:00,520 --> 00:24:04,210
A woman in the battlefield. Anyone who makes a mockery

249
00:24:04,210 --> 00:24:07,870
out of the military regulations deserves death on the spot without a recourse.

250
00:24:07,870 --> 00:24:10,820
Even if he is as high as the grand prince.

251
00:24:10,820 --> 00:24:13,230
Find Grand Prince Eun Seong.

252
00:24:15,250 --> 00:24:17,530
I will go.

253
00:24:24,670 --> 00:24:26,640
This way.

254
00:24:39,820 --> 00:24:44,460
Don't move. When everyone leaves, let's get up then.

255
00:24:52,000 --> 00:24:54,990
Now. Let's go.

256
00:25:24,080 --> 00:25:26,160
This is allium which's good for chronic disease.

257
00:25:26,160 --> 00:25:31,170
We had some already prepared so I've brought it for His Majesty.

258
00:25:31,170 --> 00:25:34,110
Thank you for your consideration.

259
00:25:35,150 --> 00:25:37,740
How is His Majesty's illness?

260
00:25:37,740 --> 00:25:42,080
He's gaining strength since he's felt better that the troops were deployed.

261
00:25:42,080 --> 00:25:45,220
Perhaps Grand Prince Jin Yang didn't feel good about being left behind.

262
00:25:45,220 --> 00:25:48,260
He left in a hurry last night as well.

263
00:25:48,260 --> 00:25:50,020
Jin Yang did?

264
00:25:50,020 --> 00:25:54,480
He said he wanted to deliver supplies to his uncle and Grand Prince Eun Seong.

265
00:25:56,070 --> 00:26:00,380
He's gone there to privately deliver military supplies?

266
00:26:00,380 --> 00:26:03,920
He must have beeen disappointed by the quick send-off.

267
00:26:03,920 --> 00:26:07,320
Is that not the love for one's blood relations?

268
00:26:13,710 --> 00:26:16,610
On our way into the battle with the Jurchens,

269
00:26:16,610 --> 00:26:20,310
you've brought a woman?  You've brought shame to the royal household.

270
00:26:20,310 --> 00:26:22,960
Enough to bring down entire military strategy.

271
00:26:22,960 --> 00:26:25,410
I followed him on my own.

272
00:26:25,410 --> 00:26:29,010
I just wanted to give him winter clothes.

273
00:26:29,010 --> 00:26:31,400
Can't you shut it? What good did you do that you're talking back like this?

274
00:26:31,400 --> 00:26:34,630
Brother, that's not it.

275
00:26:34,630 --> 00:26:36,910
Everything is my fault.

276
00:26:36,910 --> 00:26:39,500
I will sincerely accept any punishment.

277
00:26:39,500 --> 00:26:43,290
Please return Lady Ja Hyeon safely to her home.

278
00:26:44,500 --> 00:26:47,260
Do you think a war is some kind of picnic?

279
00:26:48,950 --> 00:26:54,320
You stepped over your older brother to come here in order to protect your young nephew,

280
00:26:54,320 --> 00:26:57,280
not to lose your core responsibility frolicking with a woman.

281
00:26:57,280 --> 00:26:59,200
Do you have the right to be this country's grand prince after this?

282
00:26:59,200 --> 00:27:00,840
How many times must I say it?

283
00:27:00,840 --> 00:27:03,790
His Highness did not know that I was here.

284
00:27:03,790 --> 00:27:08,780
What do we do now if a rumor spreads that a royal who should serve as a role model

285
00:27:08,780 --> 00:27:11,110
brought a woman along into the battlefield?

286
00:27:11,110 --> 00:27:12,400
That is too harsh.

287
00:27:12,400 --> 00:27:15,330
The morale of the troops would nosedive.

288
00:27:15,330 --> 00:27:17,870
I'm sure it will be the opposite.

289
00:27:18,820 --> 00:27:21,510
Who, among them, doesn't have families they've left behind?

290
00:27:21,510 --> 00:27:26,990
The younger men have loved ones they've had to tearfully say goodbye to.

291
00:27:26,990 --> 00:27:29,470
So that I could see the face of my loved one once more,

292
00:27:29,470 --> 00:27:32,240
and to keep him warm in this harsh winter,

293
00:27:32,240 --> 00:27:34,790
I sewed all night long to finish it and brought it.

294
00:27:34,790 --> 00:27:39,050
Is that such a terrible crime?

295
00:27:43,790 --> 00:27:46,610
I agree with her.

296
00:27:46,610 --> 00:27:52,230
Lady Ja Hyeon's devotion and loyalty will be a comfort to the troops.

297
00:27:57,440 --> 00:28:00,440
Please forgive my immature sister.

298
00:28:00,440 --> 00:28:05,550
I think it'd be best for everyone if I took her home right away.

299
00:28:08,910 --> 00:28:11,810
Eun Seong is not used to the military life yet.

300
00:28:11,810 --> 00:28:16,120
We will send the lady home and resolve this matter here.

301
00:28:16,120 --> 00:28:17,970
Thank you, sir.

302
00:28:19,520 --> 00:28:23,420
But I will only forgive you once.

303
00:28:23,420 --> 00:28:27,150
In future, you have to become a role model befitting of your position as a grand prince.

304
00:28:27,150 --> 00:28:29,170
I will keep that in mind.

305
00:28:29,920 --> 00:28:32,910
I will take her as soon as the supplies have been unloaded.

306
00:28:32,910 --> 00:28:35,180
That will be the safest way.

307
00:28:36,230 --> 00:28:38,660
That would be good.

308
00:28:51,010 --> 00:28:53,160
I'm sorry.

309
00:28:53,160 --> 00:28:56,710
I made it hard for you because of my rashness.

310
00:28:56,710 --> 00:28:58,970
It was not hard at all.

311
00:28:58,970 --> 00:29:06,150
I was happy you came.   And I was excited to be with you.

312
00:29:13,560 --> 00:29:17,900
Please take this, Your Highness. I'm going home anyway.

313
00:29:17,900 --> 00:29:20,840
I have another one. Take it with you.

314
00:29:30,470 --> 00:29:34,550
Tying it around makes my wrist warmer.

315
00:29:38,040 --> 00:29:42,830
I'm glad you have a guard with you.  I was worried about your return journey.

316
00:29:45,410 --> 00:29:49,220
My brother will bring you back safely.

317
00:30:03,340 --> 00:30:06,900
It's a healing ointment.  Please use it for frostbite.

318
00:30:11,880 --> 00:30:19,240
What you wanted wasn't Jo Hwi Gyeong but that girl, right?

319
00:30:19,240 --> 00:30:24,060
A hero will be richly rewarded, but she is your brother's woman.

320
00:30:24,060 --> 00:30:28,580
You must not create anything that could get in the way of your great cause.

321
00:30:29,430 --> 00:30:31,360
I thought a king is embarrassed about nothing.

322
00:30:31,360 --> 00:30:33,570
You are not a king yet.  That's why I say,

323
00:30:33,570 --> 00:30:36,660
wait until then.

324
00:30:36,660 --> 00:30:40,230
You will own everything under the sun then.

325
00:30:41,280 --> 00:30:44,730
Rumor of Hwi's conduct will spread around the capital city.

326
00:30:44,730 --> 00:30:48,410
A mentally and physically weak grand prince frolicking with a woman.

327
00:30:49,120 --> 00:30:53,660
People will know that he's not suitable to be king.

328
00:31:13,050 --> 00:31:17,080
Wait. Here. It's salt.

329
00:31:17,080 --> 00:31:21,030
Put a little bit in a water bucket, then the water won't freeze.

330
00:31:22,070 --> 00:31:24,110
Salty water makes you more thirsty though.

331
00:31:24,110 --> 00:31:25,950
Just a little bit is okay.

332
00:31:25,950 --> 00:31:29,390
It's even given to soldiers in the summertime

333
00:31:29,390 --> 00:31:30,900
to keep their strength up.

334
00:31:30,900 --> 00:31:35,030
I saw that some of the troops are not able to drink the frozen water out of the bottles.

335
00:31:35,030 --> 00:31:36,770
If there is salt, please give it to them.

336
00:31:36,770 --> 00:31:42,610
Otherwise, you should obtain some from the village before crossing the border.

337
00:31:42,610 --> 00:31:44,510
I will remember it.

338
00:32:02,190 --> 00:32:06,670
- I'll leave her in your hands. 
 - Don't worry. I will take care of her preciously.

339
00:32:06,670 --> 00:32:09,390
She's having a hard time waiting already.

340
00:32:09,390 --> 00:32:12,360
Please don't make it even harder for her.

341
00:32:12,360 --> 00:32:19,590
Forget about home.  If your memory is too strong, you cannot forge ahead.

342
00:32:31,770 --> 00:32:35,280
Brother. I'm sorry.

343
00:33:20,580 --> 00:33:22,820
Throw it away.

344
00:33:32,030 --> 00:33:35,330
Your Highness, you don't think the Royal Consort would...

345
00:33:35,330 --> 00:33:39,260
You know what the former queen and concubines have gone through.

346
00:33:39,260 --> 00:33:43,640
We have to be wary of anything served from private homes, no matter from whom.

347
00:33:43,640 --> 00:33:48,430
In Grand Prince Yang Ahn's absence, Jin Yang will want to step into the national affairs.

348
00:33:48,430 --> 00:33:49,690
Please do everything to stop him.

349
00:33:49,690 --> 00:33:55,370
His brother-in-law, Ja Joon, who's the head of security is spending money like water.

350
00:33:55,370 --> 00:33:59,190
His family is not well off but since becoming a royal brother-in-law,

351
00:33:59,190 --> 00:34:01,210
does he not know what's right or wrong?

352
00:34:01,210 --> 00:34:04,100
From where do you think he gets that money?

353
00:34:04,100 --> 00:34:06,440
Isn't that a plan to create goodwill for future use?

354
00:34:06,440 --> 00:34:13,060
Demote anyone who goes in and out of Myoung Rae palace or does business with Ja Jeon.

355
00:34:14,580 --> 00:34:21,490
They need to know that they have no future being close to Grand Prince Jin Yang with ulterior motives.

356
00:34:21,490 --> 00:34:23,680
Yes, Your Highness.

357
00:34:55,120 --> 00:34:57,560
I thought we were going straight to the capital.

358
00:34:57,560 --> 00:35:00,400
Thanks to someone, I was on the move all last night.

359
00:35:00,400 --> 00:35:03,040
I have to let my retainers eat and rest.

360
00:35:03,040 --> 00:35:04,860
Then go ahead and get some rest.

361
00:35:04,860 --> 00:35:08,990
I can go by myself if you lend me just one horse.

362
00:35:08,990 --> 00:35:11,000
The horses are also exhausted.

363
00:35:13,530 --> 00:35:17,040
Get the official servants to show this lady to a bath and  get some clothes for her.

364
00:35:17,040 --> 00:35:18,190
Yes, sir!

365
00:35:18,190 --> 00:35:22,120
No, sir. I'm fine like this.

366
00:35:22,120 --> 00:35:25,880
But I think the adults will be even more worried if you return looking like this.

367
00:35:27,400 --> 00:35:32,100
Chief Scholar entreated me to bring you back safely.

368
00:35:32,100 --> 00:35:34,470
I intend to keep my promise.

369
00:36:01,560 --> 00:36:06,610
Please enjoy your dinner alone comfortably. I will eat separately.

370
00:36:06,610 --> 00:36:09,570
Shouldn't we agree on a story to tell?

371
00:36:11,990 --> 00:36:15,590
How you ended up there, and how far you went.

372
00:36:16,930 --> 00:36:19,760
Where you slept, and what you did.

373
00:36:25,000 --> 00:36:28,400
The royal family may have already found out.

374
00:36:28,400 --> 00:36:31,300
I should at least know what happened if I am to come up with excuses.

375
00:36:35,050 --> 00:36:38,180
Not for you. For my brother.

376
00:36:40,650 --> 00:36:45,140
I just followed them as one of my brother's servants.

377
00:36:45,950 --> 00:36:47,190
Where did you sleep?

378
00:36:47,190 --> 00:36:49,650
In soldiers' barracks.

379
00:36:51,650 --> 00:36:53,880
Are you fearless or brainless?

380
00:36:53,880 --> 00:36:56,630
Prince Eun Seong was guarding me.

381
00:36:57,680 --> 00:37:01,400
Were you planning to follow him to the battlefield?

382
00:37:01,400 --> 00:37:02,890
No, Sir.

383
00:37:02,890 --> 00:37:04,300
Then?

384
00:37:04,300 --> 00:37:08,370
I was thinking of only one thing.

385
00:37:10,140 --> 00:37:15,140
I just wanted to see the grand prince for a little bit longer.

386
00:37:19,960 --> 00:37:24,530
Let's say that you stayed at the government office after sending him off.

387
00:37:26,140 --> 00:37:28,510
That's the only way to prevent defamation.

388
00:37:29,610 --> 00:37:31,100
Okay.

389
00:39:13,980 --> 00:39:16,670
I have no appetite.

390
00:39:16,670 --> 00:39:20,370
I can't even sleep when I think of my son and daughter.

391
00:39:20,370 --> 00:39:23,560
At this rate, I'm going to die before my time.

392
00:39:23,560 --> 00:39:28,430
Madam, don't be like this. Please eat a little bit more.

393
00:39:28,430 --> 00:39:33,820
You have to be strong if this household is to keep its stability.

394
00:39:37,290 --> 00:39:39,190
You ate everything.

395
00:39:40,680 --> 00:39:44,160
Madam! Madam! Please come out.

396
00:39:44,160 --> 00:39:46,080
Lady is back!

397
00:39:46,080 --> 00:39:47,930
Our Lady Ja Hyeon!

398
00:39:47,930 --> 00:39:50,070
Lady Ja Hyeon.

399
00:39:55,190 --> 00:39:58,770
Lady! Be careful, Madam.

400
00:39:58,770 --> 00:40:01,500
I'm back, Mother.

401
00:40:05,330 --> 00:40:08,040
Go out.  Go back out again.

402
00:40:08,040 --> 00:40:10,830
Madam! Madam! Madam!

403
00:40:11,900 --> 00:40:13,830
Do you think this house is an inn

404
00:40:13,830 --> 00:40:16,720
where you can leave and come back any time you want?

405
00:40:16,720 --> 00:40:20,120
Are you a man? How can you sleep outside (of the home) so recklessly?

406
00:40:20,120 --> 00:40:23,170
I'm sorry, Mother. I won't do it ever, ever again.

407
00:40:23,170 --> 00:40:24,970
Get here right now.

408
00:40:24,970 --> 00:40:27,290
Let's put an end to this, between you and me.

409
00:40:27,290 --> 00:40:28,980
Either you die or I die.

410
00:40:28,980 --> 00:40:31,840
Not even a hair of mine was hurt. I'm back safe.

411
00:40:31,840 --> 00:40:33,630
I saw that my older brother was doing well, too.

412
00:40:33,630 --> 00:40:35,640
Did I say I wanted to know that?

413
00:40:35,640 --> 00:40:39,260
My daughter leaves home to look for my son?

414
00:40:39,260 --> 00:40:41,080
Why don't you punish her officially?

415
00:40:41,080 --> 00:40:47,230
If you do it here like this, it doesn't look so good in front of the servants and all.

416
00:40:47,230 --> 00:40:51,150
Please go inside and give her the straps properly.

417
00:40:51,150 --> 00:40:53,080
How many times will you hit her?

418
00:40:53,080 --> 00:40:56,680
- Twice? Thrice?
 - Kkeut Dan!

419
00:40:56,680 --> 00:41:00,150
You are right. Get me an entire bundle of straps then.

420
00:41:00,150 --> 00:41:05,000
I will break the legs of the two of you today.

421
00:41:05,000 --> 00:41:06,650
Me? Why me?

422
00:41:06,650 --> 00:41:09,040
Because you didn't attend to your lady properly.

423
00:41:09,040 --> 00:41:11,600
Because you didn't even know when your mistress ran away in the middle of the night!

424
00:41:11,600 --> 00:41:16,840
Madam! That doesn't quite add up.

425
00:41:18,170 --> 00:41:23,290
Together in life or death because we are destined.

426
00:41:32,280 --> 00:41:37,260
I've imposed on you and the royal family.

427
00:41:37,260 --> 00:41:39,530
I didn't inform the people at the palace.

428
00:41:39,530 --> 00:41:45,320
I will keep it between just you and me, so rest assured.

429
00:41:45,340 --> 00:41:47,750
I am indebted to you.

430
00:41:49,040 --> 00:41:53,550
Did you give some thought as to matters regarding your daughter's future?

431
00:41:53,550 --> 00:41:55,900
She's my daughter.

432
00:41:56,780 --> 00:42:00,840
As her father, all I want is for her to be happy.

433
00:42:00,840 --> 00:42:04,080
Since my wife and daughter have been officially introduced to the palace,

434
00:42:04,080 --> 00:42:08,310
I see no way that her marriage into the royal family can be stopped.

435
00:42:08,310 --> 00:42:13,380
It's a matter of finding a way. And if you can't find it, you just make one anew.

436
00:42:14,470 --> 00:42:17,530
I will drop by more frequently in the future.

437
00:42:17,530 --> 00:42:23,470
I wish to listen to your good advice in these turbulent times and share war news.

438
00:42:44,940 --> 00:42:48,030
Where is His Highness? Didn't he come with you?

439
00:42:48,030 --> 00:42:49,890
The thing is...

440
00:42:51,310 --> 00:42:53,480
He went to the giseang house.

441
00:42:55,200 --> 00:42:57,570
Looks like he has an appointment with someone.

442
00:42:58,340 --> 00:43:03,180
She is called Jo Hwi Gyeong, isn't she? The one His Highness visits often?

443
00:43:05,150 --> 00:43:06,520
Don't worry about it.

444
00:43:06,520 --> 00:43:10,540
You can't know all about a man's business sitting in the women's quarters.

445
00:43:10,540 --> 00:43:13,780
Even though a gisaeng, she's useful to us in many different ways.

446
00:43:13,780 --> 00:43:17,120
It's not always about gathering strong men.

447
00:43:28,110 --> 00:43:31,760
You are returning from a long journey. Why didn't you rest at home?

448
00:43:31,760 --> 00:43:34,560
My feet led me here.

449
00:43:36,510 --> 00:43:38,800
I'm pleased, but...

450
00:43:39,420 --> 00:43:43,320
When does a girl get her heart stolen by a man?

451
00:43:44,930 --> 00:43:49,970
Thinking about it, I have never once

452
00:43:49,970 --> 00:43:53,350
tried to win a woman's heart.

453
00:43:53,350 --> 00:43:55,840
Whose heart do you want to have?

454
00:43:55,840 --> 00:44:01,350
Being born as the the king's son, court ladies were always bowing down to me.

455
00:44:01,350 --> 00:44:06,130
When I came to the gisaeng house with my friends, gisaengs were all over us.

456
00:44:06,130 --> 00:44:11,310
Out of ambition to join the royal family, even the ladies of noble families

457
00:44:11,310 --> 00:44:14,120
approached me before I could court them.

458
00:44:16,170 --> 00:44:21,040
It was a given... that women found me desirable.

459
00:44:22,000 --> 00:44:24,930
That they would approach me first.

460
00:44:36,660 --> 00:44:40,510
Gisaengs follow men with money and power.

461
00:44:40,510 --> 00:44:46,020
And there may be women who fall for handsome and smart men.

462
00:44:46,020 --> 00:44:50,430
But, though it's rare, some women fall for a man's vision.

463
00:44:51,730 --> 00:44:52,750
A man's vision?

464
00:44:52,750 --> 00:44:57,950
If a woman falls for a man's vision, she dedicates her entire life to him.

465
00:44:57,950 --> 00:45:00,300
Which aspect of me are you looking at?

466
00:45:00,300 --> 00:45:03,110
I'm looking at your future.

467
00:45:04,310 --> 00:45:10,590
If I bet on your future, won't I also gain a future?

468
00:45:32,750 --> 00:45:35,890
Sab Seung Pil Mang.

469
00:45:35,890 --> 00:45:39,740
If you win many times a loss will follow.

470
00:45:39,740 --> 00:45:44,170
If one loses a hundred times, one prepares to win, but once he wins a hundred times,

471
00:45:44,170 --> 00:45:47,670
a general will become arrogant.

472
00:45:47,670 --> 00:45:50,550
We have to wait

473
00:45:50,550 --> 00:45:53,430
and then get them in one go.

474
00:45:53,430 --> 00:45:57,940
People will suffer too much if we wait indefinitely.

475
00:45:57,940 --> 00:46:01,520
Jurchens keep coming to the villages and taking their food.

476
00:46:01,520 --> 00:46:05,350
We can't do anything about the small suffering in the name of the bigger battle.

477
00:46:05,350 --> 00:46:08,740
As a military strategy, the best way is to win without a battle.

478
00:46:08,740 --> 00:46:11,540
How about starting a negotiation prior to a battle?

479
00:46:11,540 --> 00:46:13,600
Negotiate with the Jurchens?

480
00:46:13,600 --> 00:46:19,410
I believe it's necessary if we can prevent casualties among our troops.

481
00:46:19,410 --> 00:46:24,060
If so, are you prepared to go yourself?

482
00:46:24,860 --> 00:46:30,670
Can you go in there yourself and engage in a negotiation once and for all?

483
00:46:30,670 --> 00:46:34,560
The grand prince has no prior military experience. What do you mean by once and for all negotiation?

484
00:46:34,560 --> 00:46:38,200
It's a difficult task even for the most experienced generals.

485
00:46:38,200 --> 00:46:40,890
I believe battle is the best way,

486
00:46:40,890 --> 00:46:44,550
but the grand prince wants a negotiation to avoid battle.

487
00:46:44,550 --> 00:46:47,460
Shouldn't he take responsibility for his own words?

488
00:46:48,210 --> 00:46:49,720
No he shouldn't.

489
00:46:49,720 --> 00:46:53,670
We cannot have him go through such a dangerous operation.

490
00:46:53,670 --> 00:46:56,040
I will go.

491
00:46:56,040 --> 00:46:59,620
- Your Highness! 
  - Uncle is right.

492
00:46:59,620 --> 00:47:03,270
He who speaks has to take responsibility for his words.

493
00:47:15,450 --> 00:47:20,300
You shouldn't, Sir. How can you go in unilaterally without knowing how they'll respond?

494
00:47:31,460 --> 00:47:35,470
I am going on a personal visit. It would be right to take off the armor.

495
00:47:35,470 --> 00:47:37,260
Your Highness.

496
00:47:38,810 --> 00:47:41,440
I'm going there to pay my respect as a prince of a nation.

497
00:47:41,440 --> 00:47:45,400
Even if they are Jurchens, they wouldn't pull a sword on me, would they?

498
00:47:45,400 --> 00:47:47,060
There is no guarantee.

499
00:47:47,060 --> 00:47:50,170
They've taken a lot of our people.

500
00:47:50,170 --> 00:47:55,660
They could use them as a shield in the event of a battle.

501
00:47:55,660 --> 00:48:00,500
That means we will have to kill them in order to wage a battle against them.

502
00:48:00,500 --> 00:48:03,880
We have to save our people who are now hostages.

503
00:48:03,880 --> 00:48:08,100
We cannot abandon even one person.

504
00:48:08,100 --> 00:48:11,270
I will come with you.

505
00:48:11,270 --> 00:48:12,840
That will make me feel strong.

506
00:48:12,840 --> 00:48:16,530
If you came with us, it'd be most helpful.  We wouldn't need interpreters either.

507
00:48:16,530 --> 00:48:17,970
Do you speak their language?

508
00:48:17,970 --> 00:48:20,950
I lived here with my father when I was a child.

509
00:48:20,950 --> 00:48:24,550
I used it along the way and I've not forgotten it all.

510
00:48:25,260 --> 00:48:30,170
How great this is.  I feel like I've gained a thousand horses.

511
00:48:41,980 --> 00:48:49,100
Make sure to meet the leader.  The real negotiation will be with us, not with Eun Seong.

512
00:49:10,030 --> 00:49:12,810
We will need to put a weapon in every one of their hands.

513
00:49:12,810 --> 00:49:18,780
We are smuggling the weapons.  We are also making some of them.

514
00:49:18,780 --> 00:49:20,880
It will take time.

515
00:49:20,880 --> 00:49:22,190
Since we have to do it in secret.

516
00:49:22,190 --> 00:49:25,400
Meet with the official from Goon Gi Shi.

517
00:49:25,400 --> 00:49:31,310
If we can open their storage supply, we will have our weapons.

518
00:49:31,310 --> 00:49:37,920
However, Queen Dowager is demoting everyone who comes near us.

519
00:49:39,130 --> 00:49:43,330
Don't do it yourself.  Send someone else in your stead.

520
00:49:44,300 --> 00:49:47,300
They will know what to do and take care of it.

521
00:49:49,380 --> 00:49:54,750
There is no one who doesn't become friendly given money, nor is there a door that doesn't open.

522
00:49:54,750 --> 00:49:59,280
Those inside should be taken care of by the people in charge.

523
00:49:59,280 --> 00:50:01,060
I will let them.

524
00:50:06,060 --> 00:50:08,810
Please take a break for refreshments.

525
00:50:12,630 --> 00:50:14,730
At rest!

526
00:50:15,920 --> 00:50:22,910

527
00:50:24,950 --> 00:50:29,280
How about if you have these gatherings at our house?

528
00:50:29,280 --> 00:50:31,990
I will look after them to the best of my ability.

529
00:50:31,990 --> 00:50:37,010
It can't be as good outside as what you can get in your own home.

530
00:50:45,040 --> 00:50:48,840
Are you planning on dealing with all men from outside to take care of the work?

531
00:50:48,840 --> 00:50:53,440
Are you going to flirt with men in order to bring them to our side?

532
00:50:55,180 --> 00:50:58,070
There is no need for you to act like a gisaeng.

533
00:50:58,070 --> 00:51:01,500
I know you are not happy about your husband going in and out of a gisaeng house,

534
00:51:01,500 --> 00:51:06,600
but I can't accomplish a great cause and pay attention to the fragile mind of my wife at the same time.

535
00:51:06,600 --> 00:51:09,640
I was only trying to do the best work—

536
00:51:09,640 --> 00:51:13,270
Please look after the growing members of the team

537
00:51:13,270 --> 00:51:16,040
and the servants as well.

538
00:51:17,930 --> 00:51:21,220
I will take your advice.

539
00:51:35,410 --> 00:51:38,990
- Who are you?
 - He's a prince of Joseon, Grand Prince Eun Seong.

540
00:51:38,990 --> 00:51:42,040
We've come to meet with your leader.

541
00:52:09,870 --> 00:52:13,400
Dismount the horses and walk inside.

542
00:52:20,280 --> 00:52:22,220
We have to dismount, sir.

543
00:53:18,210 --> 00:53:19,730
Please go in.

544
00:53:20,540 --> 00:53:22,800
He says you can go inside.

545
00:53:29,440 --> 00:53:31,440
I'm the interpreter.

546
00:53:34,600 --> 00:53:37,480
I'm an inter... interpre... too.

547
00:53:40,000 --> 00:53:42,880
Inter... inter...interpre...

548
00:53:44,940 --> 00:53:47,470
I know why you've invaded southward.

549
00:53:47,470 --> 00:53:49,570
It's all because you need food, right?

550
00:53:49,570 --> 00:53:52,710
If you disarm and retreat,

551
00:53:52,710 --> 00:53:56,520
we will give you 300 som (1 som is app 40 gallons) of grain as compensation (12,000 gallons).

552
00:53:56,520 --> 00:53:59,600
If you wish, we can create opportunities in the future

553
00:53:59,600 --> 00:54:03,840
to exchange food and materials from time to time—

554
00:54:06,740 --> 00:54:08,610
Something like that

555
00:54:08,610 --> 00:54:11,760
we can obtain without negotiation.

556
00:54:11,760 --> 00:54:16,310
They can obtain as much by stealing.

557
00:54:16,310 --> 00:54:19,580
That is something that is injurious to your own people too.

558
00:54:19,580 --> 00:54:22,400
The soldiers of Jurchen

559
00:54:22,400 --> 00:54:23,960
are not afraid of death.

560
00:54:23,960 --> 00:54:28,540
His soldiers are not scared of death.

561
00:54:32,540 --> 00:54:35,280
Tell me what you are looking for.

562
00:54:36,330 --> 00:54:41,270
If you can supply the grain we need until next harvest,

563
00:54:42,590 --> 00:54:44,580
we will retreat from your territory.

564
00:54:48,240 --> 00:54:54,880
If you supply grains until next harvest, they will retreat.

565
00:54:55,460 --> 00:54:57,860
Do you know who I am?

566
00:54:59,640 --> 00:55:02,660
Didn't you say you were a Joseon prince?

567
00:55:02,660 --> 00:55:06,100
That means Joseon troops have arrived already.

568
00:55:06,100 --> 00:55:09,400
We are also brave soldiers who are unafraid of death.

569
00:55:09,400 --> 00:55:11,440
However, the reason why I've come to talk to you first is

570
00:55:11,440 --> 00:55:14,780
to avoid innocent civilian casualties that will inevitably

571
00:55:14,780 --> 00:55:17,380
come from the battle between us.

572
00:55:17,380 --> 00:55:20,180
In your calculation, is there no room for the

573
00:55:20,180 --> 00:55:22,650
pain and suffering that your people will suffer?

574
00:55:24,490 --> 00:55:26,570
There is no such a thing as innocent people to us.

575
00:55:26,570 --> 00:55:29,040
They are all just soldiers

576
00:55:29,040 --> 00:55:31,520
who want to give their blood.

577
00:55:31,520 --> 00:55:36,680
All of their people are soldiers, no innocent civilians.

578
00:55:45,800 --> 00:55:48,450
His greed is excessive.

579
00:55:51,640 --> 00:55:54,610
We've just begun our negotiation.

580
00:55:54,610 --> 00:55:59,450
Look how he gave us overnight accommodation.  He's not looking for a fight.

581
00:55:59,450 --> 00:56:03,310
However, our side will not accept the demands of the Jurchens.

582
00:56:03,310 --> 00:56:05,710
Grand Prince Yang Ahn will insist on facing them head on,

583
00:56:05,710 --> 00:56:10,690
and you will be responsible for suggesting a hopeless negotiation in the first place.

584
00:56:10,690 --> 00:56:13,040
We have to lessen their demands no matter what.

585
00:56:13,040 --> 00:56:18,670
Since we are going to stay here, let's look around and see what plans we can come up with.

586
00:56:18,670 --> 00:56:22,470
How about if we go and come back, Your Highness?

587
00:56:22,470 --> 00:56:24,660
How can we sleep in the tiger's den?

588
00:56:24,660 --> 00:56:28,340
What if they kill us in the middle of the night without a sound?

589
00:56:28,340 --> 00:56:31,840
You and I must protect the grand prince

590
00:56:32,950 --> 00:56:35,180
with our lives.

591
00:56:40,090 --> 00:56:41,980
Follow me.

592
00:56:45,380 --> 00:56:47,310
Let's go.

593
00:57:57,940 --> 00:58:00,610
Are you here to pray?

594
00:58:05,700 --> 00:58:12,230
For the nation's military victory and the well being of the grand prince.

595
00:58:13,770 --> 00:58:15,590
I am here to give my offering as well.

596
00:58:15,590 --> 00:58:18,410
I will take my leave first.

597
00:58:18,410 --> 00:58:20,660
I hear you like paintings.

598
00:58:21,640 --> 00:58:26,860
We have a few drawings from Song Dynasty. Do you want to come and see them?

599
00:58:27,590 --> 00:58:32,540
The only paintings I want to see are those drawn by Grand Prince Eun Seong.

600
00:58:32,540 --> 00:58:34,330
You must open your eyes now.

601
00:58:34,330 --> 00:58:37,150
The world is wide and abounding with great works.

602
00:58:37,150 --> 00:58:41,440
The drawing of my loved one is the greatest work of art to me.

603
00:58:41,440 --> 00:58:45,730
The sun will set soon. I shall take you home.

604
00:58:45,730 --> 00:58:47,470
We came just fine on our own.

605
00:58:47,470 --> 00:58:51,540
I have Kkeut Dan with me. We will be fine going back.

606
00:58:54,130 --> 00:58:56,930
Are you going to pray to Buddha every day?

607
00:58:59,400 --> 00:59:03,600
This temple is a place with a special meaning to me.

608
00:59:03,600 --> 00:59:09,020
If you come here often with your ill intention, I will go somewhere else.

609
00:59:09,020 --> 00:59:10,190
Please don't come here.

610
00:59:10,190 --> 00:59:11,940
What should I do?

611
00:59:13,080 --> 00:59:16,530
This place is special to me as well.

612
00:59:16,530 --> 00:59:21,390
This is where I come for forgiveness each time I do something wrong.

613
00:59:22,070 --> 00:59:25,460
If you don't do anything that needs forgiving, you will be fine.

614
00:59:27,070 --> 00:59:32,450
It's not easy living... the way you've intended.

615
00:59:32,450 --> 00:59:35,390
Aren't human beings supposed to live as we're intended?

616
00:59:35,390 --> 00:59:38,000
Live as intended.

617
00:59:39,610 --> 00:59:41,630
That's a good phrase.

618
00:59:44,830 --> 00:59:48,370
Please visit Myeong Rae Palace. My wife needs company.

619
00:59:48,370 --> 00:59:51,280
If you can, come often and be her friend.

620
00:59:51,280 --> 00:59:55,260
If it's for her, I would.

621
01:00:39,280 --> 01:00:44,310
- Where did you get the Joseon dress?  Did you steal it?
 - It's my mom's.

622
01:00:44,310 --> 01:00:46,990
Is your mother a person from Joseon?

623
01:00:46,990 --> 01:00:51,210
A Joseon daughter of a Jurchen father.

624
01:00:52,180 --> 01:00:54,740
You must have some story.

625
01:00:57,260 --> 01:01:01,930
Do you have a name? What should I call you?

626
01:01:01,930 --> 01:01:05,020
- Roo Si Gae. 
- So it's Roo Si Gae.

627
01:01:05,020 --> 01:01:09,290
I'm Roo Si Gae. You?

628
01:01:09,290 --> 01:01:11,650
- Hm? 
 - What, you?

629
01:01:13,720 --> 01:01:17,860
I'm Hwi. My name is Hwi.

630
01:01:17,860 --> 01:01:21,630
Hwi?

631
01:01:25,200 --> 01:01:28,870
What's so funny? Is my name funny?

632
01:01:28,870 --> 01:01:31,070
Your name.

633
01:01:36,800 --> 01:01:40,520
  When I say your name, it sounds like when I whistle.

634
01:01:40,520 --> 01:01:43,310
  Hwi. Hwi. Hwi.

635
01:01:56,540 --> 01:02:00,730
The knot on a Joseon dress is not tied that way.

636
01:02:00,730 --> 01:02:04,660
The knot.  Over here.

637
01:02:09,130 --> 01:02:13,500
I will do it for you, so remember it next time...

638
01:02:17,310 --> 01:02:20,300
I think you misunderstood. I didn't have a different intention.

639
01:02:20,300 --> 01:02:25,020
I wanted you to wear your mother's Joseon dress properly.

640
01:02:33,900 --> 01:02:35,500
Here.

641
01:02:41,160 --> 01:02:45,290
Do it like this.  Like so.

642
01:02:45,290 --> 01:02:49,520
Through the loop like this.

643
01:03:00,360 --> 01:03:02,650
Turn it around and to the outside.

644
01:03:02,650 --> 01:03:04,670
The other way. The other way.

645
01:03:04,670 --> 01:03:06,210
This.

646
01:03:07,730 --> 01:03:09,370
Try it.

647
01:03:13,240 --> 01:03:14,740
Here.

648
01:03:14,740 --> 01:03:18,980
Your Highness, I think we should go back.  They...

649
01:03:18,980 --> 01:03:20,710
They...

650
01:03:24,290 --> 01:03:26,090
I will come back again.

651
01:03:26,090 --> 01:03:31,250
No. No, it's not like that. No.

652
01:03:40,910 --> 01:03:44,310
Is there improvement with His Majesty?

653
01:03:44,310 --> 01:03:48,940
Not enough to attend to national affairs but he is recovering.

654
01:03:48,940 --> 01:03:52,150
He fell ill when he heard of the crisis on the northern border.

655
01:03:52,150 --> 01:03:56,670
He will be able to get up once he hears of the victory from the north.

656
01:03:56,670 --> 01:04:00,750
Our job as his servants is to defeat the Jurchens as soon as possible

657
01:04:00,750 --> 01:04:03,190
so that we can make His Majesty feel at ease.

658
01:04:03,190 --> 01:04:06,300
How is the battle going?

659
01:04:06,300 --> 01:04:11,800
They will look for the right opportunity to wage one major battle.

660
01:04:11,800 --> 01:04:15,940
Grand Prince Yang Ahn is confident that he will give us the news

661
01:04:15,940 --> 01:04:17,780
of victory in due course.

662
01:04:17,780 --> 01:04:22,830
Isn't it better to initiate a negotiation first?

663
01:04:22,830 --> 01:04:25,760
It's something they will decide as they see fit at the frontline.

664
01:04:25,760 --> 01:04:31,440
They will do battle if they need to and negotiate if necessary.

665
01:04:31,440 --> 01:04:33,660
It's getting colder each day.

666
01:04:33,660 --> 01:04:38,750
If the battle gets too long, the casualties will increase.

667
01:04:49,550 --> 01:04:52,720
Why?  Do you not like the food?

668
01:04:52,720 --> 01:04:58,310
I am just impressed how you connect with women as though fated everywhere you go.

669
01:04:58,310 --> 01:05:02,040
Fated?  I told you nothing happened.

670
01:05:02,040 --> 01:05:06,780
If I hadn't barged in right at that very moment.

671
01:05:06,780 --> 01:05:08,680
Ah, how can you talk like that to someone who has a loved one?

672
01:05:08,680 --> 01:05:15,370
That's what I mean.  I thought you were a pure man whose heart was for one woman only.

673
01:05:15,370 --> 01:05:18,610
Enough of the nonsense.  Eat your food.

674
01:05:18,610 --> 01:05:21,980
I'm going to meet with the leader and have it out with him again.

675
01:05:21,980 --> 01:05:24,410
Why is he playing hard to get?

676
01:05:24,410 --> 01:05:27,360
Is he holding us hostages by chance?

677
01:05:28,310 --> 01:05:31,180
What's that?  Did something happen?

678
01:05:31,180 --> 01:05:33,940
We're in trouble. Our troops started to attack.

679
01:05:33,940 --> 01:05:35,500
What do you mean?

680
01:05:35,500 --> 01:05:38,720
His Highness in the middle of negotiation?  What do you mean attack?

681
01:05:38,720 --> 01:05:39,840
What are we supposed to do?

682
01:05:39,840 --> 01:05:40,960
It's a trap, sir.

683
01:05:40,960 --> 01:05:43,510
Grand Prince Yang Ahn set a trap for you.

684
01:05:43,510 --> 01:05:47,250
No way.  It's a misunderstanding.

685
01:05:56,680 --> 01:06:00,670
You ask for negotiation and then attack us from behind?

686
01:06:00,670 --> 01:06:02,710
What? What did he say?

687
01:06:02,710 --> 01:06:04,470
They think we betrayed them.

688
01:06:04,470 --> 01:06:07,100
We will take the grand prince.

689
01:06:07,100 --> 01:06:08,670
Yes.

690
01:06:09,590 --> 01:06:12,020
What are you doing?  Let go of me.

691
01:06:12,020 --> 01:06:13,830
Hurry!

692
01:06:16,980 --> 01:06:23,920

693
01:06:28,760 --> 01:06:33,530
♫  Believing and believing  ♫

694
01:06:33,530 --> 01:06:35,870
  Grand Prince: Drawing Love

695
01:06:35,870 --> 01:06:39,510
 Did you not hear? My brother, your loved one,

696
01:06:39,510 --> 01:06:41,160
 has died at the hands of the Jurchens.

697
01:06:41,160 --> 01:06:45,740
 Grand Prince's heart is not with me.  Go find his real loved one.

698
01:06:45,740 --> 01:06:49,670
 If you want too much, you could lose what you already have.

699
01:06:49,670 --> 01:06:55,010
 Even if he comes back, it will be after Jin Yang ascends to the throne.

700
01:06:55,010 --> 01:06:57,810
 Are you going to give me the title of saejae now?

701
01:06:57,810 --> 01:07:02,100
 You are the one who got him killed.

702
01:07:02,100 --> 01:07:04,920
  Your Highness! Your Highness!

703
01:07:18,210 --> 01:07:20,810
  Grand Prince: Drawing Love
